{{!--
  Welcome email template - sent on first login

  Required context:
  - recipientName: Name of the user (can be empty)
  - dashboardUrl: URL to the main dashboard

  Optional context:
  - organizationName: Name of the user's organization
--}}
<mj-text font-size="16px" padding-bottom="16px">
  Hi{{#if recipientName}} {{recipientName}}{{/if}},
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="16px">
  Welcome to <strong>Emergent</strong>! We're glad to have you here.
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="16px">
  Emergent helps you build and manage your organization's knowledge base. With Emergent, you can:
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="8px" padding-left="16px">
  <strong>Upload &amp; Organize Documents</strong> — Import your documents and let Emergent automatically extract key information and relationships.
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="8px" padding-left="16px">
  <strong>Discover Connections</strong> — See how concepts, people, and ideas relate across your entire knowledge base.
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="16px">
  <strong>Ask Questions</strong> — Chat with your knowledge base to find answers and insights quickly.
</mj-text>

<mj-text padding-bottom="24px">
  Ready to get started? Head to your dashboard to upload your first document or explore the platform.
</mj-text>

<mj-button href="{{dashboardUrl}}">
  Go to Dashboard
</mj-button>

<mj-divider border-color="#e5e7eb" padding-top="32px" padding-bottom="16px" />

<mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280">
  If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.
  <br /><br />
  If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:
  <br />
  <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="color: #4F46E5; word-break: break-all;">{{dashboardUrl}}</a>
</mj-text>
